### Admin API Endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000/api/admin

### Get User Profile
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Update User Profile
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/admin/profile
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

{
  "fullName": "John Smith Updated",
  "phone": "+1 (555) 987-6543",
  "company": "DispatchPro Corp",
  "bio": "Experienced logistics manager",
  "location": "Los Angeles, CA"
}

### Change Password
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/admin/change-password
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "password123",
  "newPassword": "newpassword123"
}

### Get Dashboard Stats
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Get All Users (Admin Only)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Update User Status
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/admin/users/USER_ID_HERE/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}
